{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"A few years ago,\nI felt like I was stuck in a rut,"},{"time":5000,"text":"so I decided to follow in the footsteps"},{"time":7000,"text":"of the great American\nphilosopher, Morgan Spurlock,"},{"time":10560,"text":"and try something new for 30 days."},{"time":13523,"text":"The idea is actually pretty simple."},{"time":15675,"text":"Think about something you've always\nwanted to add to your life"},{"time":18700,"text":"and try it for the next 30 days."},{"time":21897,"text":"It turns out 30 days is just\nabout the right amount of time"},{"time":25315,"text":"to add a new habit or subtract a habit --"},{"time":28031,"text":"like watching the news --"},{"time":29300,"text":"from your life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31000,"text":"There's a few things I learned\nwhile doing these 30-day challenges."},{"time":34622,"text":"The first was,"},{"time":36000,"text":"instead of the months\nflying by, forgotten,"},{"time":39000,"text":"the time was much more memorable."},{"time":42000,"text":"This was part of a challenge I did\nto take a picture every day for a month."},{"time":45596,"text":"And I remember exactly where I was\nand what I was doing that day."},{"time":51132,"text":"I also noticed"},{"time":52433,"text":"that as I started to do more\nand harder 30-day challenges,"},{"time":55786,"text":"my self-confidence grew."},{"time":57579,"text":"I went from desk-dwelling computer nerd"},{"time":59500,"text":"to the kind of guy who bikes to work."},{"time":62597,"text":"For fun!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":63869,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":65243,"text":"Even last year, I ended up hiking\nup Mt. Kilimanjaro,"},{"time":68290,"text":"the highest mountain in Africa."},{"time":70000,"text":"I would never have been that adventurous\nbefore I started my 30-day challenges."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76000,"text":"I also figured out that if you\nreally want something badly enough,"},{"time":80621,"text":"you can do anything for 30 days."},{"time":84105,"text":"Have you ever wanted to write a novel?"},{"time":86959,"text":"Every November,"},{"time":88274,"text":"tens of thousands of people"},{"time":89600,"text":"try to write their own\n50,000-word novel, from scratch,"},{"time":93705,"text":"in 30 days."},{"time":95663,"text":"It turns out, all you have to do\nis write 1,667 words a day"},{"time":100536,"text":"for a month."},{"time":102573,"text":"So I did."},{"time":104000,"text":"By the way, the secret\nis not to go to sleep"},{"time":106885,"text":"until you've written\nyour words for the day."},{"time":109530,"text":"You might be sleep-deprived,"},{"time":111000,"text":"but you'll finish your novel."},{"time":113769,"text":"Now is my book the next great\nAmerican novel?"},{"time":117447,"text":"No. I wrote it in a month."},{"time":119000,"text":"It's awful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120860,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":122526,"text":"But for the rest of my life,"},{"time":124735,"text":"if I meet John Hodgman at a TED party,"},{"time":127000,"text":"I don't have to say,"},{"time":129000,"text":"\"I'm a computer scientist.\""},{"time":131000,"text":"No, no, if I want to,\nI can say, \"I'm a novelist.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":134363,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":137749,"text":"So here's one last thing\nI'd like to mention."},{"time":140000,"text":"I learned that when I made\nsmall, sustainable changes,"},{"time":143503,"text":"things I could keep doing,"},{"time":145000,"text":"they were more likely to stick."},{"time":147247,"text":"There's nothing wrong\nwith big, crazy challenges."},{"time":150000,"text":"In fact, they're a ton of fun."},{"time":152828,"text":"But they're less likely to stick."},{"time":155250,"text":"When I gave up sugar for 30 days,"},{"time":157842,"text":"day 31 looked like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":159681,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":162009,"text":"So here's my question to you:"},{"time":164474,"text":"What are you waiting for?"},{"time":166233,"text":"I guarantee you the next 30 days"},{"time":168535,"text":"are going to pass\nwhether you like it or not,"},{"time":172159,"text":"so why not think about something\nyou have always wanted to try"},{"time":176882,"text":"and give it a shot!"},{"time":178711,"text":"For the next 30 days."}]},{"cues":[{"time":180656,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":182000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}